Class LocalAttributeMap<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.webflow.core.collection.LocalAttributeMap<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, MapAdaptable<java.lang.String,V>, AttributeMap<V>, MutableAttributeMap<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LocalSharedAttributeMap

    public class LocalAttributeMap<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MutableAttributeMap<V>, java.io.Serializable
    A generic, mutable attribute map with string keys.
